subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Jelena Jankovic defeated Ana Ivanovic, 6-3, 6-4, in round-robin play at the WTA’s season-ending Sony Ericsson Championships in Doha, Qatar. Venus Williams defeated No. 2 Dinara Safina, 7-5, 6-3, and No. 9 Vera Zvonareva defeated Svetlana Kuznetsova, 6-2, 6-3. Williams trailed by 2-5 in the first set but won five straight games. In round-robin play Wednesday, Ivanovic faces Zvonareva, Venus Williams plays Elena Dementieva, and Safina plays Serena Williams.
